# Time-Series Aggregation Tool

A web-based data aggregation and ingestion application built for industrial and IoT time-series data.  
Allows a data engineer or analyst to connect to a source database, define aggregation rules per column, and write aggregated results to a target database — all through a browser UI with real-time job progress tracking.

