## Supported Aggregation Functions

| Code   | Name               | Description                                      |
|--------|--------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| MIN    | Minimum            | Lowest value in the time bucket                  |
| MAX    | Maximum            | Highest value in the time bucket                 |
| MEAN   | Average (Mean)     | Sum of values divided by count                   |
| SUM    | Sum                | Total of all values in the bucket                |
| COUNT  | Count              | Number of data points in the bucket              |
| FIRST  | First              | Value at the earliest timestamp in the bucket    |
| LAST   | Last               | Value at the latest timestamp in the bucket      |
| STDDEV | Standard Deviation | Measure of spread around the mean                |
| MEDIAN | Median             | Middle value when sorted (50th percentile)       |
| P95    | 95th Percentile    | Value below which 95% of data points fall        |

